Over the last three years I made an independent horror film called 'Attic.' It is being released in film festivals across the US this fall and so far, the few people who have seen it, tell me it is very much like, this movie, The Changeling. Even on IMDb, it recommends The Changeling, at the bottom of the page for 'Attic.' The truth is, I've never even seen The Changeling! This is so strange, it's going to be very odd watching a movie with the same premise as mine... kinda scary, actually.
